gOE8sj_wFTJsIRuiUA">Khê hành lưỡng ngạn giai phù dung quế hoa dư hỉ toại phú thử thi - 溪行兩岸皆芙蓉桂花余喜遂賦此詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A1t-%C4%90%C3%B4-L%E1%BA%A1t/author-o6P2TdkwVUJwiHY0ASq8kw">Tát Đô Lạt</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Thi%C3%AAn-Du/Li%E1%BB%87t-n%E1%BB%AF-L%C3%BD-Tam-h%C3%A0nh/poem-kAXSQG8h5bUMBdRjj9Vfhg">Liệt nữ Lý Tam hành - 烈女李三行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Thi%C3%AAn-Du/author-t5zNl0R6g-15oc9Dd33Eqg">Hồ Thiên Du</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/S%E1%BA%A7m-Tham/M%E1%BB%99-xu%C3%A2n-Qu%E1%BA%AFc-Ch%C3%A2u-%C4%91%C3%B4ng-%C4%91%C3%ACnh-t%E1%BB%91ng-L%C3%BD-T%C6%B0-M%C3%A3-quy-Ph%C3%B9-Phong-bi%E1%BB%87t-l%C6%B0/poem-Ev5JnJZsluhtpec8dzAk9A">Mộ xuân Quắc Châu đông đình tống Lý Tư Mã quy Phù Phong biệt lư - 暮春虢州東亭送李司馬歸扶風別廬</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/S%E1%BA%A7m-Tham/author-AcWs16LhWAEAw513Kk2DnA">Sầm Tham</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-T%C3%BAc/Thu%E1%BA%ADt-ho%C3%A0i/poem-VV71m9js1bbdtwwLV_OtEQ">Thuật hoài - 述懷</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-T%C3%BAc/author-DYGad0thHvgCxK3Szp1zVQ">Trần Đình Túc</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/La-%E1%BA%A8n/T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-phi-mi%E1%BA%BFu/poem-K4MZhTjFoCOhvyQEzvgqdA">Tương phi miếu - 湘妃廟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/La-%E1%BA%A8n/author-n_6MEk2_Xxnin0yOJLakrA">La Ẩn</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
